Description :
- 5,821,948 medical instruction-response pairs 
- Knowledge-grounded : Ñontent drawn from Seamantic Scholar papers
- Spans 56 medical disciplines

- 6.7% LLM precision increase
- 22.5 to 37% improvement of hallucination detection
- Alignement LLM and experts : 92.3% on groundedness, 88.6% on factuality, and 78.4% on relevance


